# Google Slides Images

- Store all local slide images in `slides/assets/`
- Use kebab-case filenames only, e.g. `ai-competence-matrix.png`
- In YAML, reference local images from `slides/` using paths like `assets/ai-competence-matrix.png`
- Do not place slide images in the `slides/` root
- Do not use spaces, uppercase letters, or ad-hoc names for local slide images
